Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Christopher, Shin. Make your report.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.46,0:00:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.83,0:00:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But, well, it's exactly as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The dragons are behaving strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no activity\Nuntil this morning, but, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't seem to be out for blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We got fairly close to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but there was no indication they'd\Nimmediately attack if a signal was given.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.79,0:00:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like they're preoccupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like a funeral!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with the superior dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In all likelihood, they're somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's no definite proof\Nthat filth was telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure why they're acting this way,\Nbut this is a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A good opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The dragons certainly do not want\Nto let us off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:01:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If that was the case,\Nthey would have raised their siege.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Some issue must have cropped up\Nfor the superior dragons
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that temporarily takes priority over us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I must assume.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.58,0:01:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's utterly insulting.\NBut it's an insult to be thankful for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Majorca.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.75,0:01:18.08,Top,,0,0,0,,How much longer will the\Nteleportation circle take to prepare?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:21.50,Caption,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(268.8,280.8)\fs21\fnTimes New Roman}Thaumaturge\NMajorca Abbott
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.08,0:01:19.29,Top,,0,0,0,,Ah! Yes, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:21.67,Top,,0,0,0,,Um, Fu said it'll take one day\Nif we work ourselves to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so it'll take two days to complete,\NYour Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Lia addressed me! With words!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.17,0:01:32.42,Top,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFF&}Tell Fu to get it done in one day\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}without anyone dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.17,0:01:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Being this close to the princess and breathing\Nthe same air as her fills me with ecstasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Our country has already lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,On the first night, five cities\Nand the capital fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot fathom just how many citizens\Nhave been devoured by dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing we can do is flee the country
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,with only the fifteen hundred citizens\Nwe've gathered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It is entirely disgraceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But we shall escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.33,0:01:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll show those loathsome dragons\Nthey can't always have their way with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.17,0:02:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We will survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Our people, the corps,\Nand every single one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I expected nothing less from\Nthe renowned Silverware Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even your excuses for turning tail\Nwere dripping with charisma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you decided to make an appearance, filth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to pretend\NI never saw you for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but you just had to show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! What did you do\Nto the commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, hold up!\NWe already discussed this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:07.33,Caption,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(358.4,298.8)\fs17\fnTimes New Roman}Episode 10: Stakes and Cooperation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to behave yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy doesn't feel strong in the slightest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hesela. Do you think\None of those two might be him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally, Greya! It must be one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an incredibly skilled group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There are even people who are\Nstronger than Leo here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the guards?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked them to let us through,\Nand they very kindly obliged.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to lend you a hand\Nin your escape plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the gist of your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to use dragon's blood\Nas a magical energy source
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and teleport out of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's a solid plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But it won't be successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The difference in military power between\Nyou and your adversary is too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you allow us to work together with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give you detailed intel\Nabout the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Better yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:05:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can provide you a superweapon capable of\Nslaying superior dragons unassisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ragna the Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We must cooperate to take down the\Ntwo superior dragons who are our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll all die here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So his name is Ragna!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:23.50,Top,,0,0,0,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFF&}Major, give us an explanation!\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's written all over her face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk all at once!\NI can't understand a thing you're saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?\NHer Highness is losing it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to... help?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of drivel is that, filth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a stain that just can't be scrubbed\Nfrom the toilet bowl of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for us to cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't play well with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You merely use others and get them killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't your style, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get straight to the point,\Nlike you usually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we kill him? Or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my job to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't work with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to your cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time I see your face, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you too, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mad Maestro, Olto Zora.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sixth Seat of the Blood of the Wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,His primary role is managing\Nand leading military matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,His power is Chemical Synthesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He can make potent drugs\Nthat instantly kill living beings
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and drugs that hypnotize his targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He can alter his blood to create\Na vast array of compounds
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and can spray them over\Na wide area as a mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But these chemicals are instantly\Nrendered ineffective in sunlight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and silverine can stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Having that information should\Nallow you to combat against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, it's more of a nuisance\Nwhen he uses chemicals on his own forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the chemicals, his dragon army's\Npower will be multiplied several times over,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and he'll have complete and utter control\Nover his hypnotized forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, since he's a superior dragon,\Nhis own power is tremendous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he get this intel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard such detailed information\Nabout superior dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What guarantee do we have\Nthat your information is true?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was lying, you'd be able to tell,\Nwouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your very existence is so fishy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you're\Ntelling the truth or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't matter what I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a windbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's tag in another player.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hwah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hwah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, persuade the Silverware Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more up your alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and that woman are totally incompatible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You could probably spew utter garbage,\Nand her fondness for you would only grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've made up your mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to stay here and fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long from now,\NI estimate that the number of dragons
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,attacking this base will be\Nat least ten thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine thousand inferior dragons.\NA thousand medial dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,About forty to fifty will be mature dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They also have a mobile front to\Ntransport them, the Writhing Shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a high probability the\NThirteenth Seat has been mobilized too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Two superior dragons will lead them:\NOlto Zora and Taratectra.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Their military force will be total overkill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 350 soldiers here, as well as\N1,500 civilians under their protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,None will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Were the Silverware Princess\Nand her comrades in your future?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you promise to follow my orders
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and give up on Ultimatia for a short while\Nso we can escape the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use the full extent of my powers
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to make sure the humans at this base\Nescape the dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I say the full extent of my powers,\Nthat's including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Break it off with me and go back\Nto the capital by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Or stay and fight to protect the people here,\Nthen flee the country together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Silverware Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-wh-wh-what? I won't work with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,D-don't think that just because you're\Nkind of a looker that I'll listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:21.25,Top,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFF&}Earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,D-don't think that just because you're\Nkind of a looker that I'll listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You called him a stain that just can't be\Nscrubbed from the toilet bowl of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's actually very accurate, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a despicable person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He loves tormenting others\Nand gets kicks from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, he's kind of a piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I often wonder why a guy like him\Nwas even born.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I always think about how everyone would be\Nbetter off if I could just kill him already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But the one thing you can trust about him\Nis his desire to kill dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I joined forces with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:10:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided that the two of us are going to\Nexterminate dragonkind together as a team!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate... all the dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hunting dragons is my forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm better at it than\Nanyone else in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Use me, Silverware Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I can help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's with that facial expression?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I make her mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The man she fell in love with at first sight\Nis ardently pleading her to use him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And she is just barely resisting\Nscreaming, "Yes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not agree, Princess Lia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That man is undoubtably a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the kind of degenerate who puts up\Nphotos of his crush all over his bedroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he does! I can always\Nsniff out other freaks like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I know for a fact he's depraved!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ragna is her first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know how to act around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And she can't allow herself to look like\Na pathetic simp in front of the corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, consequently...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I accept your proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But do not be mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm temporarily borrowing your power\Nfor strategic purposes and nothing more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I d-d-didn't make this decision because of\Nany personal feelings I have for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not be mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That was like a bad tsundere impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny, filth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That really tickled my funny bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a fan of being called\Na piece of shit,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll let it slide since the\NSilverware Princess had me in stitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't tell you to call me a piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a positive thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's better than them\Nbeing outright hostile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But still... I just don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious, Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What about my fight with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That will have to be postponed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:12:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A most excellent decision,\NSilverware Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll certainly pulverize those vile dragons\Nwith our combined forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,First, let's modify the plan\Nbased on my intel-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll cough up the information\Nabout the dragons, and that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be the one doing the planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That sure takes a load off my shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just please do make sure\Nyour plan has no holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a pain for me to have to\Npatch them later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then riddle me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A few hours ago, something about\Nthe dragons sieging us changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know what happened to them, tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because we fought against\Nthe Winged Monarch in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably going into a frenzy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and rushing off to the capital\Nright about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we even keep you around,\Nyou senile old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no excuse I can give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the progenitor now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The progenitor is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've lost control of time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've said it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultimate power that you get from\Nsomeone else is fickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Nebulim not to let anyone enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He let me waltz right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You clearly must have threatened him\Nand forced your way in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave at once! I'm not in the mood\Nto chitchat with you n-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, c'mon now. Did you actually forget\Nwhat you sent your errand boy to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the person who killed Trois?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not convinced?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:14:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think a lowly hunter\Ncould've killed that dumb windbag, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this guy was at the bottom of\Nthe barrel when it came to strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but he had a good death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess what he said right before he croaked?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding amusement in the\Nlast words of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,who suffered while dying\Nis in such poor taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But to me, pretty much everyone else\Nin the world is insignificant trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.79,0:14:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't faced many opponents\Nwho wowed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And what was this guy's attitude\Nwhen he looked death in the eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a weakling, yeah.\NBut he was a dragon hunter to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you ain't interested, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just keep his last words\Nbetween me and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how 'bout this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the dragon hunters\NI dealt with had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The craftsmanship is crude for a sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but the amount of silverine infused in it\Nand its chilling power is bananas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I have to grip it with everything\NI've got or my hand gets numb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,P-please get that thing away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be all shook up by it. Look, see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,St-stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I said stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you playing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're holding it. The sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to tell you why\Nyou can't control time anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"God is disappointed in my worthless,\Npathetic self," aren't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NIt's nothing as dramatic as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason you can't control time is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you've lost in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic is a means to change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You need three things to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You need the magical power\Nto create change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You need the process that gives\Ndirection to that change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And lastly, you need the confidence to control\Nthe change once it's been actualized.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you're saying it's a mental problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet every time you use magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the image of your enemy\Nsurges through your mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That enemy could move even though\NI made the world fall still!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I did not give him\Npermission to move,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,he attacked me while time was stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno why he didn't stop moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But the reason everything else won't stop\Nis because you've lost in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Winged Monarch? What a laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, your heart is too beaten down\Nto rule over anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more like Traumatia now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Traumatia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I need to do to use\NTime Control Magic again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:16:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta forget your fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You were afraid of it at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but then you grabbed it without faltering\Nand cut me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For a second, you forgot your fear\Nbecause of the rage you felt towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget my fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget my fear of the enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act like it's so easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was that straightforward,\NI wouldn't be struggling like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Command me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Command me to obliterate\Nthe source of your fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and your fear will be a thing of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I won't command you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Losing my Time Control Magic is simply\Nmy own personal failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't use you, my greatest weapon,\Nto get my power back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, the top priority is\Nto annihilate this country
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:18:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so the world can be shaped as God desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my sole duty as\Nthe Winged Progenitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't want the answer\NI should use to ace the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you really want.\NWhat you truly desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What you really want me to do is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,get revenge, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how 'bout I tell you\Nwhat I really want first?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It enrages me that some bastard\Ntried to kill my woman while I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when did I become your woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will you insist on clowning around\Nand making a fool of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't intend on listening to me,\Ngo ahead and fight! That's fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to fight because you ordered me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna bow and scrape\Nbecause you're the progenitor
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or worship you like some saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:19:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, you're just an unhinged woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,An unhin-?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.00,0:19:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm following this unhinged woman\Nof my own volition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't give a rat's ass about God,\Nor allegiance to our blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,or any of that garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can act however you want around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can piss and moan about your problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can blow your top and bawl your eyes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be selfish like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, I can take it all.\NI'll always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-there's no way\NI can allow that for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a duty to my God and bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And above all, I have a duty to the\Nimmense number of people we've killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My personal desires-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't doubt that those are\Nyour true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not what I'm trying to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you want me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring... me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:19:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is their fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of it! I'm so sick of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot bear it any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it that we're the only ones who suffer\Nwhile they get to continue living?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simply not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an order, Woltekamui!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the full extent of your\Nphenomenal fighting prowess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rip off their heads and bring them to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Attagirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wish is my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Ultimatia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Tia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't there when you really needed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sorry for making you worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right! Nebulim!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This oaf threatened you into letting him\Ninto my chamber, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The kiddo said it was totally cool\Nfor me to go in. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFF&}You liar!\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}It is true, Lady Ultimatia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFF&}Nebulim would never disobey my orders.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}It is true, Lady Ultimatia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFF&}Nebulim would never disobey my orders.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}I let Kamui walk right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFF&}He's a good boy, unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFF&}He's a good boy, unlike you.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Given the state you were in,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:34.21,Top,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFF&}You shouldn't set such high expectations\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}for kiddos, ya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew only Kamui's words\Nwould get through to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:37.63,Top,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFF&}You have some nerve trying to admonish me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do to get closer to\NLady Ultimatia's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do to get closer to\NLady Ultimatia's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As close as he is to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Reaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,will...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,hunt you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy really got my hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:22:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When was the last time I felt\Nthis pumped to fight someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.17,0:22:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And an opponent I've never even seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When we finally face down, let's have a fight\Nto the death that'll go down in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddaya think, Reaper?
